➜【股票入门】选股的四要六放弃
http://www.sohu.com/a/418691996_498954	5646
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>【选股四要】</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">1、要选小市值股票。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200916/daf64717a7b44fc4b0b3c11bbd424b6c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">2、选无解禁股的股票</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3、要选无再融资压力的股票</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">4、要选有“生育能力”的股票</p>
<h1 class="ql-align-justify"><strong>【选股六放弃】</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-justify">1、舆论关注的股票要放弃</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">2、没走出底部的股票要放弃</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3、移动筹码分布图上筹码很分散的股票要放弃</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">4、前期大幅炒高的股票要放弃</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">5、未来没有成长性的股票要放弃</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">6、量能技术指标不良的股票要放弃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200916/466b62ebff8b492088a34d04b052b7ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
